IVYMX - AXON IVY Java Management Extension 1.0.0 API

Annotations and utility classes to register POJO's as JMX MBeans.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
com.axonivy.jmx
Annotations and utility classes to register POJO's as JMX MBeans.
com.axonivy.jmx.util
Utility classes that simplifies the implementation of MBeans.
Annotations and utility classes to register POJO's as JMX MBeans. To start have a look at the class MBeans and the annotation MBean.

Simple Example:

  @MBean("GettingStarted:name=Person")
 public class Person
 {
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
     Person person = new Person();
     MBeans.registerMBeanFor(person);
   }
 }
